name: grid.wtf
description: The GRID is creating a MM-OS (money-making operating system), tools to engage, analyze, and participate in streaming, prediction markets, real-time news, pokemon, crypto, stocks and more. We also have an AI agent that uses our database of information/aggregation to help guide you through whatever market you want to put your money in. As a user navigates our app they will get insights and flows into what's happening in the market in real time from multiple markets all within one interface.
